<div xmlns:perseus="http://www.perseus.org/meta/perseus.rdfs#" xmlns:dctype="http://purl.org/dc/dcmitype/" xmlns:tufts="http://www.tufts.edu/" xmlns:alph="http://alpheios.net/namespaces/tei" class="alpheios-lex-text_container en">
    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n1937" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βρί̄θω</span></b>  (root <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βρι</span>), ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βρῖθον</span>, aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔβρῑσα</span>,
          perf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βέβρῑθα</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">be heavy,
            weighed down;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">σταφυλῇσι μέγα βρί̄θουσα ἀλωή</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 18.561</span></i>, and once mid., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μήκων καρπῷ βρῑθομένη</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 8.307</span></i>; with gen., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ταρσοὶ τῡρῶν βρῖθον,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Od. 9.219</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">
            τράπεζαι σί̄του βεβρίθᾱσι</span>, etc.; met., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔρις βεβρῑθυῖα</span> (= <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βρῑθεῖα</span>), <i><span class="en">Il.
          21.385</span></i>.—Also <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">fall heavily upon, charge</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 12.346</span></i>, etc.; <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">preponderate, be
            superior</span> (by giving the most presents), <i><span class="en">Od. 6.159</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
    <div class="alpheios-lex-alph-source">From <u>
            <u>A Homeric Dictionary</u>
        </u> (Georg Autenrieth, New York, Harper and Brothers, 1891) </div>
